data.text:
2011: Appeared in eight games in the defensive back rotation, starting in one...made nine tackles (four solo) on the year, with 0.5 TFL and two pass break-ups...recorded two tackles against Morgan State (11/5)

2010: Appeared in three games for the Wildcats in 2010, logging two tackles as a cornerback in a 23-10 win at North Carolina Central (10/23)

2009: Played in one game in his rookie season at B-CU vs. Winston Salem State (10/24)

High School: Helped Godby post an 18-2 regular season record and trips to third round of playoffs his junior and senior seasons ... 2007 track team won state title
